<a name='toc_2'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>2.Test Suite : orir3584_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testeaza functionalitatea de adaugare a unui produs nou in stocul magazinului</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc28875"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-5: AddProductTestCaseECP1&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">orir3584</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>[ECP]&nbsp;Test Case 1: Adaugarea cu succes a unui produs -&gt; clasa valida<br />
<br />
exemplu valid: (101, &quot;Spanish Latte&quot;, 12.75, SPECIAL_COFFEE, PLANT_BASED)<br />
<br />
Rezultat asteptat -&gt; Succes (Produsul este adaugat cu succes in stoc)<br />
<br />
<br />
&nbsp;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>ID -&gt; numar intreg, 1-9999<br />
Nume -&gt; string, 3-100 caractere<br />
Pret -&gt; numar real, 5.0-45.0&nbsp;<br />
Categore -&gt; o categorie din CategorieBautura = {&nbsp;CLASSIC_COFFEE, MILK_COFFEE, SPECIAL_COFFEE, ICED_COFFEE, TEA, BUBBLE_TEA, JUICE, SMOOTHIE, ALL }<br />
Tip -&gt; un tip din TipBautura = {&nbsp;BASIC, DAIRY, LACTOSE_FREE, WATER_BASED, PLANT_BASED, POWDER, ALL }</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.Product.AddProductTest1</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.Product.AddProductTest#validECPTest</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">orir3584_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc28877"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-6: AddProductTestCaseECP2&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">orir3584</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>[ECP] Test Case 2: Adaugarea invalida a unui produs -&gt; clasa invalida<br />
<br />
exemplu invalid: (102, &quot;Matcha&quot;, -50.00, SPECIAL_COFFEE, DIARY)<br />
<br />
Rezultat asteptat -&gt; Eroare (pret invalid, produsul nu este adaugat in stoc)</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Datele de intrare a atributelor unui produs nu sunt valabile / conforme domeniului lor de definitie</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
