<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.Product.AddProductTest2</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >MyDrinkShop.Product.AddProductTest#invalidECPTest</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">orir3584_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
