<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">orir3584</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>[BVA] Test Case 1: Adaugarea cu succes a unui produs la pretul minim valid -&gt; limita inferioara valida<br />
exemplu valid: (102, &quot;Matcha Latte&quot;, <strong>5.0</strong>, MILK_COFFEE, PLANT_BASED)<br />
